# Skills Auto-Invoke — {{module.name}}

## Principle

Skills codify patterns. Implementing without a skill violates consistency.

## Protocol

**Before creating any file:**
1. "Does a skill in `.claude/skills/` cover this artifact?"
2. "Does a rule in `.claude/rules/` define the pattern?"
3. If YES → invoke skill or follow rule
4. If NO → evaluate creating a skill

